Package model.entity

Class Graph

java.lang.Object
model.entity.Graph
public class Graph
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents a Graph. A Graph has a user and a list of booleans which represent the wins and losses. It has methods to calculate the heights of the points in the graph.
Version:
22/5/2021
Author:
Riccardo Giacalone (ricardo.giacalone@students.salle.url.edu), Guillermo Gonzalez (guillermo.g@students.salle.url.edu), Oscar Cubeles (oscar.cubeles@students.salle.url.edu), Goddy Clinton (weriwohmbang.g@students.salle.url.edu)
